The
woman's
words
came
with
an
intense
earnestness
which
carried
conviction
with
them.
"Is
this
true,
Barrymore?"
"Yes,
Sir
Henry.
Every
word
of
it."
"Well,
I
cannot
blame
you
for
standing
by
your
own
wife.
Forget
what
I
have
said.
Go
to
your
room,
you
two,
and
we
shall
talk
further
about
this
matter
in
the
morning."
When
they
were
gone
