yellow
light.
"I
wonder
he
dares,"
said
Sir
Henry.
"It
may
be
so
placed
as
to
be
only
visible
from
here."
"Very
likely.
How
far
do
you
think
it
is?"
"Out
by
the
Cleft
Tor,
